title: Home Is Where the Heart Is
Moment of Doubt
description: When a serial killer is arrested on information provided by a psychic. The man hires Maggie Zombro to defend him. He tells her that the evidence they found was not where he left it. And eventually Dicky suspects the cop who arrested the man of not doing things by the book, but chooses not to say anything.

title: Try to Be Nice, What Does It Get You?
Legacy
description: Tess' boyfriend Asher tries abduct a man but is stopped. He reveals he was trying to bring the man to Israel because he's a Nazi. Tess tries to help him but it appears the man was granted asylum by the U.S. because he gave them information on the Russians during the Cold War.

title: Sister, Can You Spare a Dime?
